{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu}} 13th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|684 AD|ja|684th year}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日}} ) – Established the eight types of surnames: Mahito, Asomi, Sukune, Kisune, Dōshi, Omi, Ren, and Inaoki. {{要出典|date=2021-04}} * {{ill|Shuchō|ja|朱鳥}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|686 AD|ja|686th year}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日}} ) – {{ill|Prince Ōtsu|ja|大津皇子}} was captured by Crown Prince {{ill|Kusakabe|ja|草壁皇子}} on suspicion of treason. * {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|770 AD|ja|770th year}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日}} ) – By the presentation of Suikime, the era was changed from {{ill|Shingokeiun|ja|神護景雲}} to Hōki. * {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|770 AD|ja|770th year}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日}} ) – The grandson of {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|天智天皇}} , Prince Shirakabe, ascended to the throne as the 49th Emperor, {{ill|Emperor Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇}} . * {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Itsukushima|ja|厳島の戦い}} took place, with the forces of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|Mōri Motonari}} defeating those of {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢}} . * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 15th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1587 AD|ja|1587th year}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日}} ) – The Kitano Grand Tea Ceremony was held in Kyoto’s {{ill|Kitano Tenmangū|ja|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine}} precincts, where {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi}} , with tea masters {{ill|Sen no Rikyū|ja|千利休}} , {{ill|Tsuda Sōkyū|ja|津田宗及}} , and {{ill|Imai Sōkyū|ja|今井宗久}} , presided over a gathering of 1,000 participants. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō}} 19th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1614 AD|ja|1614th year}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康}} ordered various daimyō to mobilize, marking the beginning of the Osaka Winter Campaign. * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1673 AD|ja|1673rd year}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日}} ) – The {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国藩}} constructed the {{ill|Kintaikyo Bridge|ja|錦帯橋}} .
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日}} ) – {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1521 AD|ja|1521st year}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Mitsunari|ja|石田三成}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1560 AD|ja|1560th year}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日}} ) – {{ill|Konishi Yukinaga|ja|Konishi Yukinaga}} , a Christian daimyō (born circa {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year}} ?). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日}} ) – {{ill|Angokuji Eikyū|ja|安国寺恵瓊}} , a military commander (born circa {{ill|1539 AD|ja|1539th year}} ?).
