{{Lunisolar October|qq=}} 
'''October 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|12=draft}} . 


== Events ==
* {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|qq=|12=draft}}  13th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|684 AD|ja|684th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – Established the eight types of surnames: Mahito, Asomi, Sukune, Kisune, Dōshi, Omi, Ren, and Inaoki. {{要出典|date=2021-04|qq=}} 
* {{ill|Shuchō|ja|朱鳥|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|686 AD|ja|686th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Prince Ōtsu|ja|大津皇子|qq=|12=draft}}  was captured by Crown Prince {{ill|Kusakabe|ja|草壁皇子|qq=|12=draft}}  on suspicion of treason.
* {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|770 AD|ja|770th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – By the presentation of Suikime, the era was changed from {{ill|Shingokeiun|ja|神護景雲|qq=|12=draft}}  to Hōki.
* {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|770 AD|ja|770th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The grandson of {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|天智天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , Prince Shirakabe, ascended to the throne as the 49th Emperor, {{ill|Emperor Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Itsukushima|ja|厳島の戦い|qq=|12=draft}}  took place, with the forces of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|Mōri Motonari|qq=|12=draft}}  defeating those of {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}}  15th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1587 AD|ja|1587th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The Kitano Grand Tea Ceremony was held in Kyoto’s {{ill|Kitano Tenmangū|ja|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|qq=|12=draft}}  precincts, where {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=|12=draft}} , with tea masters {{ill|Sen no Rikyū|ja|千利休|qq=|12=draft}} , {{ill|Tsuda Sōkyū|ja|津田宗及|qq=|12=draft}} , and {{ill|Imai Sōkyū|ja|今井宗久|qq=|12=draft}} , presided over a gathering of 1,000 participants.
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}}  19th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1614 AD|ja|1614th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|12=draft}}  ordered various daimyō to mobilize, marking the beginning of the Osaka Winter Campaign.
* {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1673 AD|ja|1673rd year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国藩|qq=|12=draft}}  constructed the {{ill|Kintaikyo Bridge|ja|錦帯橋|qq=|12=draft}} .

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1521 AD|ja|1521st year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Mitsunari|ja|石田三成|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1560 AD|ja|1560th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Konishi Yukinaga|ja|Konishi Yukinaga|qq=|12=draft}} , a Christian daimyō (born circa {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year|qq=|12=draft}} ?).
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Angokuji Eikyū|ja|安国寺恵瓊|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander (born circa {{ill|1539 AD|ja|1539th year|qq=|12=draft}} ?).


