* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Mitsunari|ja|石田三成|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1560 AD|ja|1560th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Konishi Yukinaga|ja|Konishi Yukinaga|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Christian daimyō (born circa {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ?).
