qq=draft}} , presided over a gathering of 1,000 participants. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 19th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1614 AD|ja|1614th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ordered various daimyō to mobilize, marking the beginning of the Osaka Winter Campaign. * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1673 AD|ja|1673rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} constructed the {{ill|Kintaikyo Bridge|ja|錦帯橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
