lianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|770 AD|ja|770年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/770 AD|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} ) – By the presentation of Suikime, the era was changed from {{ill|Shingokeiun|ja|神護景雲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shingokeiun|qq=}} to Hōki. * {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōki|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|770 AD|ja|770年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/770 AD|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} ) – The grandson of {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|天智天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Tenji|qq=}} , Prince Shirakabe, ascended to the throne as the 49th Emperor, {{ill|Emperor Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kōnin|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1555 AD|qq=}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 16|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Itsukushima|ja|厳島の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Itsukushima|qq=}} took place, with the forces of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|Mōri Motonari|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mōri Motonari|qq=}} defeating those of {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tōharaken|qq=}} . * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 15th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1587 AD|ja|1587年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1587 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 1|qq=}} ) – The Kitano Grand Tea Ceremony was held in Kyoto’s {{ill|Kitano Tenmangū|ja|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitano Tenmangū|qq=}} precincts, where {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}} , with tea masters {{ill|Sen no Rikyū|ja|千利休|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sen no Rikyū|qq=}} , {{ill|Tsuda Sōkyū|ja|津田宗及|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuda Sōkyū|qq=}} , and {{ill|Imai Sōkyū|ja|今井宗久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imai Sōkyū|qq=}} , presided over a gathering of 1,000 participants. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 19th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1614 AD|ja|1614年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1614 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} ordered various daimyō to mobilize, marking the beginning of the Osaka Winter Campaign. * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enpō|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1673 AD|ja|1673rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1673 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakuni Domain|qq=}} constructed the {{ill|Kintaikyo Bridge|ja|錦帯橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kintaikyo Bridge|qq=}} .
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1555 AD|qq=}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 16|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tōharaken|ja|陶晴賢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tōharaken|qq=}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1521 AD|ja|1521st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1521 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 6|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Mitsunari|ja|石田三成|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishida Mitsunari|qq=}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1560 AD|ja|1560年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1560 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 6|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Konishi Yukinaga|ja|Konishi Yukinaga|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konishi Yukinaga|qq=}} , a Christian daimyō (born circa {{ill|1555 AD|ja|1555年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1555 AD|qq=}} ?). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600 AD|ja|1600年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600 AD|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 6|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Angokuji Eikyū|ja|安国寺恵瓊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Angokuji Eikyū|qq=}} , a military commander (born circa {{ill|1539 AD|ja|1539年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1539 AD|qq=}} ?).
